snippet.title: The Rewired Soul
snippet.description: We constantly consume content in such a passive way, but this is a form of escapism and way to not look at our own lives. I believe that everything we watch or hear about in pop culture or the news should be something we analyze and do some introspection. My channel is dedicated to social commentary with a solution so we can try to turn some of the mess into a message.
